	   <a name=9746553801359></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9746553801359><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=9746553801359>Kills per level, Kills per bubble</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=9746553801359#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Nov 19th 12:36 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Using the formula from Giddygonzalus we can find out how many kills you will need per level to get to the next level.&nbsp;&nbsp;Also, you can find out how many kills it takes to gain 1 bubble of exp.  I used (X*X*X*C*R*L/MOB*MOB*75)where X = your level and MOB= black con (same level) or the average of blue, black and yellow MOBs.  The 75 considers MOBs outside,not in dungens or planes. (See previous post by Gedran for all the details)  Anyway this gives you the exp you need per level, and then just divide that by 6 (which looks like the amount of bubbles in the level bar) to find out how many kills you need to get a bubble.  Here is an example for Halfling Druid levels 14-30. (*Note the extra amount of kills needed for the first hell level 30)<br><br>I hope I didn't use any "fuzzy Math". If I am wrong please correct, but dont spam.<br>(Level, Experience per Level, Experience per Bubble)<br><br>L  E/L E/B<br>14 180 30<br>15 192 32<br>16 204 34<br>17 216 36<br>18 228 38<br>19 240 40<br>20 252 42<br>21 264 44<br>22 276 46<br>23 228 48<br>24 300 50<br>25 316 53<br>26 329 55<br>27 342 57<br>28 353 59<br>29 365 61<br>30 418 70<br><br>Hope this helps<br><br>Philo<br>7th Hammer<br>level 14 druid<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%>
	   <a name=97467704023871></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97467704023871><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=8&mid=97467704023871>RE: Kills per level, Kills per bubble</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=8&mid=97467704023871#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
