	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have rooted, dotted and blasted many many mobs to death without them ever breaking root.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sometimes it is resisted completely.. and other times it only lasts a few seconds.  It's completely random.  The idea is simply to try to get an advantage.  And as for harmony, it is never resisted, is not seen as a hostile act, and your mana bar does move faster if you have harmony cast on yourself while medding.  I've tried it and have tracked the movement of the bar with harmony cast and without.  <br><br>Just sharing what works for me.  Feel free to do what you like with it.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
