	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can have more than one Concordance or Arcane Research (the book you get from Gypsies for GLS).<br>These books are actually containers, much like the Tome of Vanear binder. You cant place a container in a container, so if your have no containers and your inventory full of GLS you can trade them 4 at a time for 4 books. If you overfill your inventory by turning in GLS the other books drop on the ground.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
