	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sorry, I should mention that "wisp island" is the island where 5 willowisps spawn.&nbsp;&nbsp;To get there, you take the boat from Qeynos.  It think the zone is called Kerra Ridge or Kerra Isle.<br>You can find an abundance of wisps in other zones, especially North Karana, where they litter the area.  It's great hunting there, as the guards are close and the gypsy camp is there too, so you can to the quest and trade the lightstones in.  Just watch out for getting aggroed by animals, Hill Giants, griffons and especially Grimfeather, who flies at SOW speed.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
